Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.73,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,LENGAN BAJA BERAPI BIRU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Pahlawan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat berangkat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, aku kapok bertualang denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan katakan hal sesedih itu, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal kita belum sampai\Nke tambang yang dimaksud, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau sadar, jangan hobi membuat masalah\Nsetiap hari, dasar Pahlawan Dungu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:00:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cantik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona cocok memakai gaun itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari gunakan gaun ini di hari-H.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku, memakai baju biasa\Njuga sudah cukup, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda harus menggunakan pakaian\Nyang mencerminkan keluarga Aquarain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa tidak terlalu berlebihan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona tidak suka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada tamu yang ingin menemui Nona.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku datang tiba-tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin bertanya soal sihir pemulihan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, tumben memakai baju seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak sama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sangat cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kaget karena jarang melihat Cecilia\Nberpakaian layaknya seorang bangsawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melakukan perjodohan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Serius? Bukankah kau...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya mematuhi perintah Raja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan bertemu untuk sekali ini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak berniat untuk menikah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku masih perlu banyak berlatih.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Latihan? Kau sedang mengejar apa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kapan kalian bertemu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiga hari lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mikana juga mengenal orang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia anggota Party Pahlawan\Ndari Kadipaten Luminaria...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebuah kehormatan bisa bertemu dengan Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Soleil Graceheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Cecilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama tidak bertemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita terakhir bertemu saat pesta perayaan\Nkekalahan Raja Iblis. Betul?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Betul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah mendengar dari Raja Darts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa kau tak berniat melakukan pernikahan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menolak lamaran dari berbagai pihak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena aku masih perlu banyak berlatih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini daun teh yang berkualitas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bisa menikmati teh selezat ini
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena Nona berhasil mengalahkan Raja Iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan aku, tapi kekuatan Tuan Pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia pasti akan mengatakan\Nsemua berkat bantuan rekan-rekan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, sifat itulah yang membuatnya\Nmenjadi pahlawan sesungguhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi mengalahkan Raja Iblis,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada pahlawan yang dipilih\Ndengan mengutamakan kekuatan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tentu mengenal Pahlawan Miller\Ndari Kekaisaran Gallis, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu ini hanya rumor belaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}konon dia ditahan di wilayah kekaisaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, kenapa tiap negara\Nmembentuk Party Pahlawan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Cecilia... Ralat, mungkin\Npara bangsawan mengetahui alasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan saat umat manusia\Nhampir dibinasakan ras iblis,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}para raja di berbagai negara pun\Nberlanjut pada konflik perebutan kekuasaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:06:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa sesama manusia\Nbegitu enggan saling membantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sependapat denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untungnya, Raja Darts sungguh bijak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beliau mengkhawatirkan tanda-tanda\Nkonflik yang muncul di negara sekitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maka dari itu pula,\Nbeliau mengabulkan permintaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melalui pernikahanku dan Nona Cecilia,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}orang-orang akan mengetahui\Nbahwa Kadipaten Luminaria
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Kerajaan Clariness adalah sekutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bisa membatasi negara lain\Nyang memiliki niat jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Cecilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menikahlah denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, mari kita bersama
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengantarkan kedamaian pada seluruh dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat sibuk menggali,\Nkami malah mengenai sarang monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Imut banget, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menggemaskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini masalah besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saking berbahayanya,\Naku tak bisa memakai beliung.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya, kami meminta petugas\Nmenghubungi Tuan Pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau bisa mengurus mereka\Ntanpa terluka sedikit pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Serahkan pada kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Youki, aku harus apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa bertanya padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal kau yang menerima misi ini\Ndengan penuh percaya diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya Youki selalu memberi saran bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir, kau akan memikirkan\Nide bagus juga kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya kau tak punya rencana apa-apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, skala pembicaraannya\Nterlalu besar, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya Nona Cecilia belum memahami\Nbetapa pentingnya dirimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku terdengar berlebihan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi akulah yang masih banyak kekurangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih perlu banyak latihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari tunda percakapan soal pernikahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku sudah tinggal di Minerva\Nsejak beberapa waktu lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang mempelajari\Nnegara ini dan rakyatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa... kau melakukan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai bangsawan,\Nkita perlu mengenal negara lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kita saling memahami\Nkondisi masing-masing negara,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pasti bisa menghindari\Nkonflik yang tak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maka dari itu, ini sekadar permintaanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama Nona Cecilia sempat saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maukah kau mengajari aku
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tentang negara ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Niat Soleil benar-benar mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ini bisa membantu mempererat\Nhubungan dengan Kadipaten Luminaria,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku siap membantu dengan senang hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku menceritakan sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tentang... Cecilia yang dijodohkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang apa tadi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo? Youki belum mendengar apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saking kagetnya,\Naku sampai menemui Cecilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cecilia, jangan menerima perjodohan itu.\NTolak saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini perintah dari Baginda Raja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan! Cecilia, tolaklah permintaan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yuuga, kalau ingin merengek,\Nlakukanlah di depan Raja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau dia dijodohkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya, pasangannya Soleil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soleil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia anggota Party Pahlawan\Ndari Kadipaten Luminaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemampuan berpedangnya\Nmungkin setara Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pewaris wilayah besar, pintar,\Ndan juga sopan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, lanjutkanlah misinya sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Youki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia tak bercerita padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada perlu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Begini, aku mencari Yuuga...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mikana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang kebingungan karena\Ntak bisa mengerjakannya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sendiri? Warga sipil ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Youki tiba-tiba saja pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa bisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kuceritakan perjodohan Cecilia, dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yuuga, kau sudah tahu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah. Ternyata Mikana juga tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang akan dilakukan orang itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini panti asuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bunda Suci!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, aku memanggang kukis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hore!\N- Ada kukis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, jangan lupa\Nberterima kasih pada Bunda Suci, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bunda Suci, terima kasih, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagikan dengan adil, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bunda Suci, ceritakan sesuatu, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, ah. Aku mau menggambar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebentar, satu-satu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita makan kukisnya dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak siapa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pembantu Bunda Suci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soleil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bohong.\NAndai saja aku bisa membantu lebih...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gendong aku yang tinggi, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gendong yang tinggi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal sudah dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soleil, gendonglah dia\Ndengan kedua tanganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, angkatlah dia ke atas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggi, tinggi sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asyik, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya giliranku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Soleil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama kau tidak capek saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa kau bisa menggendong anak lainnya juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, mari melakukannya bergiliran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soleil, terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak-anak sangat bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan masalah, aku sendiri\Nmendapat pengalaman tak tergantikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya seperti itu\Ncara bermain dengan anak-anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa anak-anak di Kadipaten Luminaria\Ntidak seperti mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sendiri tak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai pewaris keluarga Graceheart,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku selalu belajar dan berlatih ilmu pedang\Nsedari kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang pun, aku terus belajar\Ndi samping ayahku,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sehingga tak sempat bertemu langsung\Ndengan rakyatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, saat terpilih\Nmenjadi anggota Party Pahlawan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan berangkat ke luar\Nuntuk mengalahkan Raja Iblis,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}setiap harinya penuh dengan kejutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tertawa dengan kencang,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}marah, dan sangat jujur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah bertemu dengan rakyat,\Naku semakin ingin melindungi mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah itu dari Raja Iblis,\Natau kesulitan-kesulitan lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melindungi, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terdengar sombong, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku juga selalu mengusahakan\Nhal yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga pernah meminta tolong\Npada orang yang sangat kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, dia selalu membantu\Norang yang kesulitan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahkan tanpa kuminta terlebih dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia orang yang hebat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin menjadi orang\Nyang pantas berada di sampingnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga punya seorang panutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soleil juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kita sama-sama\Nperlu banyak berlatih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak untuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, tolong ajari aku lagi besok...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentang negara ini dan rakyatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu, jika aku bisa membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, sampai bertemu besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kulakukan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku gagal menolak tawarannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan bekerja keras sebagai petualang,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan setelah aku bisa hidup dengan mapan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah memutuskan akan\Nmenyatakan perasaanku sekali lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Youki yang sekarang
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah punya banyak teman\Ndan terlihat bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.31,0:16:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bukan Youki yang tak bisa\Npergi ke luar Istana Raja Iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin dia sudah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menghapus kehadiranku\Ndan pergi ke tempat Cecilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vanish Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Api biru...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kusangka bisa bertemu\Nras iblis saat berpatroli.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bermaksud memburu manusia\Ndi tengah kegelapan malam?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lengan Baja Berapi Biru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lengan Baja Berapi Biru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membakar kejahatan\Ndengan api kebajikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak punya waktu untuk meladenimu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ras iblis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk apa kau muncul di sini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin apa setelah bertemu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takkan kubiarkan lari!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menghilangkan apinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada ribut-ribut apa ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau... Buronan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, dia ras iblis, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada ras iblis yang muncul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dia ada di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan biarkan ras iblis\Nmasuk ke wilayah Minerva!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergi kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ras iblis!\N- Kenapa dia datang ke sini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Si-Silakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suamiku mengirimkan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa aku bereinkarnasi menjadi ras iblis?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini punya Clayman, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Youki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pendekar Pedang Sihir Kilat Hitam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menjadi buronan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semalam, ada ras iblis\Nyang menyelinap masuk ke Minerva.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untungnya, kita berhasil mengusirnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sementara ini, kita akan menambah\Npersonel patroli untuk bersiaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua, harap waspada!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekian pidato dari Komandan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gerbang akan dibuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yakin tak perlu memeriksa perorangan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iblis yang muncul punya tanduk dan sayap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama penampilannya tak mencurigakan,\Nbukan masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Youki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cecilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Cecilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soleil?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin perasaanku saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi pria itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu... Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengenal orang itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu luka dari mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan banyak bergerak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Cecilia, apa kau sudah selesai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar, kalian saling mengenal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Youki, dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami hanya kenalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku seorang petualang yang sering dia bantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena Cecilia baik pada semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bahkan membantu orang sepertiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf terlambat mengenalkan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Soleil Graceheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang ingin menikahi Nona Cecilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Youki, begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang tak bercerita padamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf. Aku sudah mengganggu kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga hari kalian menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Telah terjadi kasus yang merepotkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kuharap kau mau bekerja sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Irene, kuserahkan pengawalan\Nwilayah ini padamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian ini, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, aku sedang serius, tahu.
